thread.title: Jameis Winston draws reaction after telling youngsters 'ladies are supposed to be silent'
thread.title_full: Jameis Winston draws reaction after telling youngsters 'ladies are supposed to be silent'

author: Mark Inabinett | minabinett@al.com
title: Jameis Winston draws reaction after telling youngsters 'ladies are supposed to be silent'
text: Tampa Bay Buccaneers quarterback Jameis Winston said he "used a poor word choice" when he said ladies are "supposed to be silent" while speaking at a Florida elementary school on Wednesday.
